onstants.php#constant.false">false</a></span></strong>。  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 changelog" id="refsect1-function.imageistruecolor-changelog">  <h3 class="title">更新日志</h3>  <table class="doctable informaltable">       <thead>     <tr>      <th>版本</th>      <th>说明</th>     </tr>    </thead>    <tbody class="tbody">     <tr> <td>8.0.0</td> <td>  <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">image</span> 现在需要 <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.gdimage.php" class="classname">GdImage</a></span> 实例；之前需要有效的 <span class="literal">gd</span> <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.resource.php" class="type resource" style="color:#EAB766">resource</a></span>。 </td></tr>    </tbody>     </table> </div> <div class="refsect1 examples" id="refsect1-function.imageistruecolor-examples">  <h3 class="title">示例</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><div class="example" id="example-2888">    <p><strong>示例 #1 使用 <span class="function"><strong>imageistruecolor()</strong></span> 简单检测真彩色实例</strong></p>    <div class="example-contents"><div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#1E1F22;"><blockquote style="border:1px gray solid;white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br></span><span style="color: #FF8000">// $im 是图像实例<br><br>// 检查图像是否为真彩色图像<br></span><span style="color: #007700">if(!</span><span style="color: #9876AA">imageistruecolor</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$im</span><span style="color: #007700">))<br>{<br>    </span><span style="color: #FF8000">// 创建新的真彩色图像实例<br>    </span><span style="color: #9876AA">$tc </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">imagecreatetruecolor</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">imagesx</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$im</span><span style="color: #007700">), </span><span style="color: #9876AA">imagesy</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$im</span><span style="color: #007700">));<br><br>    </span><span style="color: #FF8000">// 复制像素<br>    </span><span style="color: #9876AA">imagecopy</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$tc</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #9876AA">$im</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #9876AA">0</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #9876AA">0</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #9876AA">0</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #9876AA">0</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #9876AA">imagesx</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$im</span><span style="color: #007700">), </span><span style="color: #9876AA">imagesy</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$im</span><span style="color: #007700">));<br><br>    </span><span style="color: #9876AA">$im </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">$tc</span><span style="color: #007700">;<br>    </span><span style="color: #9876AA">$tc </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">NULL</span><span style="color: #007700">;<br><br>    </span><span style="color: #FF8000">// 或者使用 imagepalettetotruecolor()<br></span><span style="color: #007700">}<br><br></span><span style="color: #FF8000">// 继续使用图像实例<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">?&gt;</span></span></blockquote></div>    </div>   </div>   </div> <div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-function.imageistruecolor-seealso">  <h3 class="title">参见</h3>  <ul class="simplelist">   <li><span class="function">{@link imagecreatetruecolor()} - 新建真彩色图像</span></li>   <li><span class="function">{@link imagepalettetotruecolor()} - Converts a palette based image to true color</span></li>  </ul> </div></div>
